{
  "stem": "198.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I wasn't home, and I thought, I would never, never see my parents again.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But, at the last minute, they released me from work, and I met my parents at the place where we were gathered.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And just the way I was dressed with nothing, they told us [SOBBING] to give all the money, all the jewelry, all our possessions.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Poland was divided to a reich and protectorate.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They sent us to the protectorate, which was about maybe 100 miles from the city I was born.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was very cold.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Old people who were dying.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Young children were freezing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We were marching for days and days until we got to the protectorate.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We came, it was a city.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I don't know how you say it in Polish, it was Lowicz.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "A lot of people were gathered in the city.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It was very cold with no food, epidemic, dirt, no facilities.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "People were dying of typhus.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "After a while, I was young, and I saw that's not the life for me, so I remembered I have relatives in Lodz, so I went to the train.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I jumped a train and went back to a Lodz.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "All of a sudden, on the train-- it was my sister, my youngest sister and I.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "All of a sudden I see on the train, it was a lot of a panic going on.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I realized that the Germans came and they wanted to get all the Jews.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I jumped a train.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was maybe 10 miles before Lodz, and I walked into Lodz-- With your-- with your sister, or by yourself?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With my sister.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We jumped a train, I don't know how I did it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I guess when you're young, you don't know what you're doing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You just do it.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
